This is IdleScripter open repository

This App is used to run Apple Scripts when computers foes into idle.

You can setup "Time interval" which will be used like "Idle interval", and two apple scripts. One when computer idles and one when you start working with it.

Example Apple scripts will be included soon.


All questions, bug-reports or feature-requests point directly to marek.sebera@gmail.com / marek@msebera.cz

